Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the cherry blossoms are in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going flower viewing at a shrine's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And the weather's great too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect weather for a flower viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those lunches would be perfect in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really {\i1}would{\i0} go for dumplings over flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor, how about we go look around and get our fortunes told and you spread out a sheet and save us a space?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:19.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only the light of deductions can tear apart the pitch-black shadows and bottomless darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conflicting info under the cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mysterious case and the FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:24.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:29.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I just {\i1}had{\i0} to get "bad luck", didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got "fairly good luck"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got "good luck"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got "delayed luck", which isn't too great...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go tie up our fortunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You managed to get good fortunes, so you should take them home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:24.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shigemori Sakamaki (66)\NFlower Viewer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:26.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You only tie up your fortune to leave bad fortune behind and change your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though in recent years, some people have taken up the bad habit of tying up whatever fortune they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s the only one who has to tie up his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You just {\i1}had{\i0} to peek at it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what did you get, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I can live without knowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're so interested, then I guess I'll just have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Great luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about swapping with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, "bad luck" is really rare, so I hear some people take getting it as a sign of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So don't feel disappointed, Cool Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you here to see the flowers too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! I love cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called her out here so you to could talk in secret, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, parks and shrines are often used by spies to exchange information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why don't we give them some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they want to have a private talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You often find Public Safety Officers watching places like this, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you saw Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with a burn scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was at that bank robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.21,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.68,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:45.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that you, Shū?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tell me it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.21,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A burn scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but Bourbon, one of the men in black, in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wandering around like that near people who knew Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to check whether or not Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was truly dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since if the FBI had faked his death,\Nhe'd know by your reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though on the Bell Tree Express, Vermouth wore the Akai disguise herself, instead of applying it to Bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Bell Tree Express... You mean {\i1}they{\i0} were behind that train bombing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that man with the burn scar was one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...then that means Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the next time I see that man with the burn scar prancing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch him, rip off his disguise and find out who he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as where you can find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He calls himself Tōru Amuro, and he works part-time at Café Poirot under the Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know... That's why I had you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have the FBI investigate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should have achieved his objective, so why is he still at Poirot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that foreign lady who was a hostage in that bank robbery just like me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:55.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tōhei Benzaki (35)\NFlower Viewer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:55.43,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was one row behind you to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:08:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it was my wife who covered up your eyes and mouth with tape, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I do, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then was that man with a burn scar next to you your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not... But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, if he isn't, then don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him two or three days ago, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?! Where did you see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pickpocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a pickpocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You alright, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine... I was just panicking since someone put their hand in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you do often find pickpockets lurking in crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:55.63,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ikuyo Yatani (50)\NFlower Viewer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:56.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... You're right. I'll have to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You can't drink that water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to gently rinse out your mouth, then spit it out on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? You still can't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where you saw him, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was stuck in bed all day yesterday with this cold, so my memory's fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} have a very hoarse voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you rinse your mouth with this water too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want anyone to catch my cold, and I washed my hands earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have seen him by a can vending machine selling coffee by any chance, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did he like canned coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he often drank it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even back when we were expecting them to attack the hospital at any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Have you seen that man before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's an agent recently stationed here to increase security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not too good remembering friendly faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I'd never forget an enemy mugshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, it's no surprise that you've seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're both FBI agents, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:33.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But looking at him makes me feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He must've been tired to drop his coffee like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, what do you mean by an attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy wasn't the burnt man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact me if you remember, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:17.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On the Bell Tree Express, Bourbon said that he was sure Akai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:21.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would he disguise himself as Akai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What goal could he have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, don't ring it so loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Dad said I should ring it with all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:56.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yoriko Dan'no (29)\NFlower Viewer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:55.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You ring these bells to tell the gods that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So if you don't ring it loud enough, the gods might not notice you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's give it a great big ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What sort of man was that Akai guy you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling he greatly resembles someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're probably just imagining it!\NBesides, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a big ruckus about it behind the toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's terrible, Shin'ichi! A murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just witnessed a murder taking place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You witnessed a murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyway, come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a big crowd forming, so it won't be hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Did you see the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They were shaded by the trees,\Nso I could just see a silhouette,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but they were attacking again and again\Nwith a rod about 30 centimeters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A 30 centimetre-long rod... Death by beating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey... Let me through! Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's that woman...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the lady who ran into {\i1}Sensei{\i0} earlier!{***do we really want to use Sensei? me: Jodie}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been long since she was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five yen coins colored black with a marker pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be Kurobee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurobee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the nickname of a pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was named that because she puts three black five yen coins in the bags of her victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:10.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:10.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumor goes that the "five" of five yen, the "black" of the pen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:14.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}san
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the "three" for three coins can be read as "gokurosan",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:18.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}gokurōsan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it's like she's saying "thank you" to her victims for earning her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, it's here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Step away from the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Jodie Starling, an FBI agent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,FBI?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seal the exit to this shrine right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And call for detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she was murdered by Kurobee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had a purse full of black five yen coins in her bag, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably {\i1}was{\i0} Kurobee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this bundle of notes wrapped in a rubber band that was in her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside it... Is that a GPS transmitter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a phone, you can locate it to within five metres.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for a pickpocket to have that wrapped in notes in her wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that one of her victims murdered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just do this, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be an FBI agent, but this is Japan, and you're only here because you took a day off to fly over here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go ordering around the Japanese police, think about how it looks for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My usual habits just took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the crime scene's quite far from the shrine exit, and it hasn't been that long since she was murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so since I had the shrine exit sealed, her murderer should be trapped here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, well, I guess you did help by giving the right orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this woman really the pickpocket Kurobee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Division Three of the Criminal Investigation Department have spent years looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The purse she had was filled with five yen coins colored black with a marker pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurobee is said to leave three black five yen coins in her victims' bags...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And did you really see Kurobee get beaten to death, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I witnessed it when passing by after leaving the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was dark with the shade from the trees, and at first I thought they were hammering in a post or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what did her killer look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I really saw was their silhouette...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though they were wearing a hat, and holding a thin rod about 30 centimeters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they have any other unusual traits?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Now you mention it, they were dragging their feet slightly as they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even called out to them and asked if they were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dragging their feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ignored me and walked away, and by the time I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that they had been beating this woman, they'd already mixed in with the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, if they were dragging their feet at a situation they should want to run away from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. I doubt it would be an act to try and avoid suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:18:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to find the killer among all the people at this shrine with so few clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nearly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be able to narrow it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman had something strange in her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A GPS transmitter wrapped in banknotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why would she have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pickpocket Kurobee has never been caught, so there's no way of identifying that it was her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,other than finding black five yen coins in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if someone deliberately had notes with a transmitter stolen by her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they could track her with a mobile phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wait for Kurobee to go somewhere quiet, and then beat her to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then the killer is one of Kurobee's victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, pickpockets often commit thefts in groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we can't ignore the possibility of\Nher killer being one of her accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Kurobee was working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She herself yelled out that there\Nwas a pickpocket here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a common tactic used by pickpockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you heard there was a pickpocket nearby, you'd check your wallet was safe without thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pickpockets use it to find where\Ntheir victims keep their wallets,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if she had accomplices, wouldn't she have one of them yell out instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, I think you'll find that your wallet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wallet's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably took it when you helped her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, if the pickpocket's dead, then how are we going to find her victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that shouldn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in a bin by the racks to tie up your fortunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I found one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in a bin by the place I drank the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh! I think I've got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in a bin by where we rang the bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked a priest to help get it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got one from a bin near the crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rubbish was about to be collected, but I made a fuss and had it searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, then bring the wallets you've found over here, making sure not to get fingerprints on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.33,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! The wallets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pickpockets just take the money out of wallets, then abandon them, so if we check those wallets...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may be able to find their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:38.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these four were the only wallets you found in the bins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rubbish collector said that he'd started collecting the rubbish from the bin I checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that blue wallet's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that makes you a suspect too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never left our side after that woman bumped into her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't have a chance to murder anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is likely the owner of one of the other three wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, it's easy to tell who owned this black wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a driving license in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw that guy earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He talked with Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cold, so he was wearing a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I doubt we'll find licenses so easily in the other wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photo sticker?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know that lady too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She taught us how to ring the bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's still over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the final red wallet is empty except for a "pretty good luck" fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'll be able to tell who owned that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it belong to that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us to take our good fortunes home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him take out that red wallet to buy his fortune when he was lined up in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did think it was a bit flashy for a guy like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You know who owned it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're dealing with a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you go with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If any of them have a 30 centimetre-long rod, then that'll be the clincher, but well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know soon enough even if they don't have a rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer left three black five yen coins by the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as if to say "you can have them back"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be easy to find distinctive black five yen coins like these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then whoever doesn't have the black five yen coins that Kurobee gave them would be the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This detective said you wanted to talk to us right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you supposing we've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I ask you for your statements, could I ask each of you to check if you have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,five yen coins colored black with a marker pen in your pockets or bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five yen coins colored black?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:23:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have anything that weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are these here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I found some black five yen coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! B-But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez. All {\i1}three{\i0} of them have their coins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly are these creepy black five yen coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, they're souvenirs left by\Na pickpocket known as Kurobee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? No way! Then I was pickpocketed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I noticed I didn't have my wallet just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to take them to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.78,0:24:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have much in my wallet, so I don't mind losing it, but have you caught that pickpocket then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.69,0:24:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found her dead body not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:25:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we suspect her killer is one of you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.24,0:25:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.51,0:25:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're victims ourselves, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.14,0:25:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, we'd like to conduct body checks on each of you, and inspect your belongings and phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's at your discretion, so you can refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.24,0:25:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do, it may cause trouble later, so we'd advise you to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.70,0:25:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.60,0:25:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspect whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my phone's all sticky since I've got greasy skin,\Nso if you want to check it you'll have to put up with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.15,0:25:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.60,0:25:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.47,0:25:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.31,0:25:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking of the men in the video you took before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, when we were trying to identify the spy they sent to infiltrate the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you deliberately dropped a phone and had them pick it up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fat man who picked it up first had greasy skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:26:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end, the next man to pick it up was the spy, and the last old man had a pacemaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.13,0:26:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's the phone that Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.79,0:26:11.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10　回想　\Nねえ　僕の知り合いのおじさんの→\N\Nビートルに乗せて運ばない？}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.38,0:26:14.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10　回想　\Nねえ　僕の知り合いのおじさんの→\N\Nビートルに乗せて運ばない？}Why don't we put her in a Beetle an old friend of mine drives?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.12,0:26:18.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10（ジョディ・ジェイムズ）え？\N後部座席なら寝かせられるし→}We can lay her down on the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.10,0:26:24.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10その悪い人たちは　きっと\Nストレッチャーが乗せられる→\N\N大きい車で運ぶって\N思ってるだろうから→}Those bad guys probably think you'll carry her in a bigger vehicle on a stretcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.60,0:26:26.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10絶対にバレないと思うよ。}They would never guess this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.80,0:26:29.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10（ジョディ）\Nそ　そうかもしれないけど...。}T-That's probably true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.11,0:26:32.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10じゃあ僕　外に出て電話で呼ぶね。}Then I'll give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.57,0:26:34.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10すぐ来てくれると思うから。\Nあっ　ああ...。}He'll probably come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:40.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10いくらボウヤでも\Nそいつは出来ない相談だ。}No matter how smart you are, this isn't an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.26,0:26:43.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10これは我々　ＦＢＩの仕事。}This is a job for the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.36,0:26:49.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10（赤井）これ以上　一般市民を\N巻き込むわけにはいかん。}We can't let any more civilians get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.59,0:26:52.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10ああ　で　でも...。}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.01,0:26:54.22,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(0,700)後は我々に任せるんだ。}Just leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.27,0:26:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.99,0:27:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That doesn't matter at all right now, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.77,0:27:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just feeling the shock from finding out the man with the burn wasn't Shū.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.80,0:27:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta pull myself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.46,0:27:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.56,0:27:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sounded worried all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.79,0:27:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.11,0:27:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how about it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.29,0:27:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is any of those three the killer you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.25,0:27:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that old man with a cane does look very suspicious, but the murderer had a 30 centimetre-long rod, not a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.57,0:27:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hat the killer was wearing wasn't a hunting cap like the old man is wearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.87,0:27:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or a knit cap like that woman is wearing, but something like an alpinist's hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.62,0:27:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the murderer didn't have a cough like that man there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.23,0:28:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But couldn't he just be faking his cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.52,0:28:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we first met him, he had no way of knowing that we knew the doc, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.05,0:28:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have had to pretend to have a cold in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.88,0:28:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.65,0:28:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about the way they walk, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.80,0:28:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said they dragged their feet slightly, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without his cane, it looks like the old man can't walk at all, let alone drag his feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.66,0:28:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the other two don't seem to be dragging their feet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.28,0:28:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You can't find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.44,0:28:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you checked everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.30,0:28:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We even checked the drain of the purification trough and inside the offering box.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.10,0:28:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of those three were carrying it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.95,0:28:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. We checked the old man's cane, but it doesn't seem to have been used as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.10,0:29:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we checked all of their phones, but none of them had any app that could track a GPS transmitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.35,0:29:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though the killer could've predicted they'd be checked, and deleted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.15,0:29:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.14,0:29:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we'd need a warrant to conduct any further checks...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.33,0:29:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.07,0:29:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you met those three, were\Nany of them acting strangely?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.53,0:29:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acting strangely?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.39,0:29:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, if they had someone following them, who handed them some sort of thin rod?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.30,0:29:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.35,0:29:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man told us that if we drew good fortunes, we should take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.90,0:29:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman said that we should ring the bells loudly so that the gods can hear us when we ring them!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.28,0:29:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other man said he already washed his hands at the purification trough,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he must've been at the shrine for quite a while before meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.52,0:29:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.30,0:30:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believe we've found the killer's hat and coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.36,0:30:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.67,0:30:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've got blood splatters on\Nthem, so there's no mistaking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.10,0:30:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're covered in flower petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.51,0:30:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. They appear to have been hidden under the fallen cherry blossom petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.75,0:30:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the weapon might be hidden in the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.15,0:30:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find it even if you have to kick through the petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.58,0:30:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.28,0:30:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they made such a pretty pink carpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.94,0:30:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. They may be small by themselves, but when many petals fall, they're almost like a pink carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:44.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see! So that's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.35,0:30:47.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why that person said {\i1}that{\i0} to the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.81,0:30:53.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means the reason they dragged their feet was probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.48,0:30:58.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You may have grasped the truth of this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:01.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I doubt you'll figure out the truth behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.55,0:31:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you planning on keeping us here‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun's already setting!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.33,0:31:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don‭'‬t care whether there‭'‬s a case going on‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.19,0:31:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's got nothing to do with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.44,0:31:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! Please wait just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.78,0:31:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.65,0:31:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting difficult to keep the shrine's exit sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.14,0:31:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.39,0:31:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any luck with the murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.95,0:31:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it hasn‭'‬t been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.11,0:31:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the killer already escaped with the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.40,0:31:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.‭ ‬Taking into account the time between the murder and when we‭ ‬sealed the exit, and that the culprit was dragging their feet‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.48,0:32:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very likely that the killer's still on the grounds of this shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have hidden the roughly ‬30‭ centimetre-long rod that Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.79,0:32:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the three people who were pickpocketed are the best suspects after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.14,0:32:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.‭
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.17,0:32:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since we found a GPS transmitter hidden in notes in the wallet of the murdered pickpocket‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.13,0:32:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be like Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said ‬—\hthe killer let their wallet with the GPS transmitter get stolen,‭ ‬tracked the thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.89,0:32:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and killed her in a deserted location.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.86,0:32:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But none of those three seem to\Nhave any problem with their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it seems that old man needs his cane to walk, not because his feet are hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we assume that the killer had an accomplice and slipped them ‬the murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.23,0:32:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we would have to search everybody who‭ ‬came to this shrine to watch the flower blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.33,0:32:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.28,0:32:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one part of the murder weapon that the killer still has on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.98,0:33:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One part‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.00,0:33:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,‭ ‬that‭'‬s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.57,0:33:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer used it to tie‭ ‬together the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.96,0:33:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tie together?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon you saw was in one piece,‭ wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't tied together or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.71,0:33:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer ‬constructed the murder weapon using a‭ ‬large quantity of a certain object.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.35,0:33:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if you find the many parts,‭ ‬they‭'‬re hidden in such a way that they aren‭'‬t suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.30,0:33:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Approaching the children,‭ they managed to camouflage their actions smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.86,0:33:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.89,0:33:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the old man who talked to us when we were drawing fortunes‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That‭'‬s true,‭ ‬there were a lot of fortunes tied up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.57,0:33:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody would notice if there were a few more of them,‭ ‬right‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.19,0:33:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter how you tie fortunes together,‭ ‬you can'‬t make a weapon that can beat a person to death,‭ can you‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.80,0:33:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}are{\i0} paper, after all‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.75,0:33:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you mean that man‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.65,0:33:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man who refused the ladle Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} tried handing him when we were washing our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.54,0:34:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That‭'‬s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.28,0:34:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were lots of ladles at the purification trough!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.05,0:34:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you slip a ladle with an iron handle in there‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.99,0:34:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police would have found‭ ‬that,‭ ‬don‭'‬t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.31,0:34:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying that there was no such ladle in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That only leaves the lady we met\Nwhen we were ringing the bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.12,0:34:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were only two bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.96,0:34:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn‭'‬t you guys do something else before ringing the bell‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.29,0:34:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That‭'‬s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.42,0:34:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The offering‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.75,0:34:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We threw in a five yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.63,0:34:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Into the offering box‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.18,0:34:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:40.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}goen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the saying‭ "May you‭ ‬find good ties and good fortune‭",
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.00,0:34:42.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}goen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.00,0:34:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,most of the offerings are five yen coins,‭ ‬which have a hole in the centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.94,0:34:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.‭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.80,0:34:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‬If you pass a wire or string through the hole and bind a lot of coins together, you get a long rod‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.85,0:34:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, even if you find a large quantity of five yen coins in the offering box afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.08,0:34:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they‭'‬re mixed up with the other offerings and not suspicious‭,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.91,0:35:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which means it easily deceives the police,‭ ‬who are looking for‭ ‬a long metallic rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.01,0:35:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But,‭ ‬in order to produce a ‬30‭ ‬centimetre-long rod‭, ‬you‭'‬d need around‭ ‬200‭ ‬five yen coins‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.24,0:35:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if you throw such a large quantity of coins into the box, you‭'‬ll stand out and people around you will certainly notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.36,0:35:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why the‭ ‬killer approached the children‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.42,0:35:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying the gods wouldn't hear them if they didn't ring the bell loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.22,0:35:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.69,0:35:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.70,0:35:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.00,0:35:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found her through a GPS transmitter in the wallet you had stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.16,0:35:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then bashed her to death with a rod made from many five yen coins tied together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer of Ikuyo Yatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, or rather the pickpocket Kurobee, is none other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.97,0:35:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.50,0:35:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.11,0:35:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.42,0:36:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found her through a GPS transmitter in the wallet you had stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.75,0:36:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then bashed her to death with a rod made from many five yen coins tied together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer of Ikuyo Yatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, or rather the pickpocket Kurobee, is none other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.08,0:36:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoriko Dan'no{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.07,0:36:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called out to the kids to ring the bell loudly to hide the noise of lots of five yen coins clanking into the offering box.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.29,0:36:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You untied the knot tying the five yen coins together, then holding onto the end of it and dangling it over the offering box,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.80,0:36:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you could get rid of all the five yen coins in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.65,0:36:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more,‭ ‬the murder occurred before you rang the bell‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.09,0:36:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning that as a victim of the pickpocket,‭ your wallet must already have been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‭ ‬The fact that you apparently made an offering and rang the bell without noticing that is proof that you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:37:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should certainly have noticed that your purse had been stolen when you tried to take it out to make an offering‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don‭'‬t you know‭ that you shouldn‭'‬t open your wallet in front of the offering box‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.21,0:37:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the gods see the contents of your wallet,‭ it might anger them,‭ ‬because you have so much and yet put in so little.‭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.12,0:37:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‬That is why I always put a five yen coin into my pocket before visiting a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why you didn't notice your wallet had been stolen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.20,0:37:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,‭ if you'd seen me put a large amount of five yen coins into the box, that might mean something,‭ ‬but like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.45,0:37:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I didn‭'‬t see it,‭ ‬I can be sure‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.99,0:37:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...if we take a look at your shoelaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.16,0:37:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, you used one of your shoelaces to tie the coins together‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.24,0:37:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you‭ ‬couldn‭'‬t immediately flee from the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.45,0:38:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of your shoelaces was missing, so you'd have lost your shoe if you'd walked normally‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that you put your shoelace back in and tied it after ringing the bell,‭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if you used that shoelace for ‬committing the crime‭, it should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.87,0:38:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's blood, that spurted when you killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.71,0:38:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.72,0:38:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found bloodstains.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.69,0:38:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did she still have her black five yen coins‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.00,0:38:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren‭'‬t the five yen coins beside the body the ones that Kurobee had left in your pocket when she stole the wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.20,0:38:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were the coins I showed to you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.30,0:38:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what were those coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:39:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones left behind were the ones I found in my pocket when I was pickpocketed last year‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.34,0:39:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The five yen coins that killed my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.37,0:39:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.79,0:39:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the one on the photo in your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.43,0:39:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.21,0:39:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wallet that was stolen ‬last year also had my car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.53,0:39:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I didn‭'‬t have them anymore,‭ ‬my son,‭ ‬who had asthma, ‬was locked in the car for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.56,0:39:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‬By the time we got‭ ‬to the hospital,\Nit was too late, and he died‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.99,0:39:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I researched that pickpocket on the net and hung out in places where she frequently appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.54,0:39:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you put that photo in your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.54,0:39:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it hadn‭'‬t been in your wallet, we might not have known it was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.26,0:39:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you open the wallet, the photo leaps into your sight,‭ ‬doesn‭'‬t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.60,0:40:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted that pickpocket to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.23,0:40:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That what she stole wasn't just money‭,\Nbut also the life of a little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,‭ ‬does that mean I'm free to go‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.59,0:40:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.64,0:40:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then may I go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.44,0:40:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may need to hear your testimony on the pickpocketting case later though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.85,0:40:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.89,0:40:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.45,0:40:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.75,0:40:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to have bad eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.17,0:40:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when that pickpocket lady\Nsaw your face,‭ ‬she was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.98,0:40:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that's because she stole your wallet earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.77,0:40:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why didn't you say anything at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.87,0:40:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been your second time meeting her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.48,0:40:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That‭'‬s it!‭ ‬My eyesight is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.07,0:41:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your eyesight is bad you should wear glasses, or you won‭'‬t see the cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.69,0:41:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to the flower viewing‭ by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.03,0:41:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I came to buy a good luck charm‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.29,0:41:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.61,0:41:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It‭'‬s for me,‭ ‬isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.55,0:41:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Motoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the little one, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.68,0:41:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.51,0:41:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An easy childbirth good luck charm‭!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.05,0:41:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn‭'‬t I tell you to relax at home‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.75,0:41:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to look for you because I was worried when you didn‭'‬t return!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.15,0:41:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then were you the person who taped me up during the bank robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.03,0:41:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, were you the foreigner from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.32,0:41:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I‭'‬m so sorry.‭ But we were threatened, so I had ‬no choice‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.02,0:41:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.95,0:42:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.42,0:42:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife‭'‬s condition isn‭'‬t very good.‭ ‬Would it be okay if I left‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.10,0:42:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.61,0:42:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning sickness is a condition that you have in the first stages of pregnancy,‭ ‬right‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.21,0:42:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though looking at her size, the pregnancy should be in the sixth month already‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.80,0:42:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,‭ ‬the nausea could also be caused by something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.31,0:42:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,‭ ‬that‭'‬s‭ ‬right, Camel‭.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.40,0:42:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the guy with the burn wasn't Shū.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.83,0:42:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a decoy that they planted in order to find out whether Shū really died, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.00,0:42:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah,‭ ‬Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}‭...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.47,0:42:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway,‭ ‬I‭'‬ll tell you the details once I‭'‬ve returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.90,0:42:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the money's gone,‭ ‬but if you could check the contents of your wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.54,0:42:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.94,0:42:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cards are all there, as are the contents of the pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.80,0:42:57.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is from during that department store bomb threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.86,0:43:03.62,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.62,0:43:05.54,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The edge of the coaster's bent...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.91,0:43:12.00,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Run! This area's dangerous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.17,0:43:15.55,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.39,0:43:18.35,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.77,0:43:21.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shū...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.08,0:43:28.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that guy with the scar isn‭'‬t Shū, then who wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.20,0:43:30.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.90,0:43:35.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sorry, Agent Jodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.55,0:45:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with you? If you sleep here, you'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.21,0:45:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.41,0:45:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! He's just sleeping from having too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.59,0:45:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother can‭'‬t hold his liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.08,0:45:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.90,0:45:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.35,0:45:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man you disguised‭ as had his wallet stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.38,0:45:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} find it strange that he didn‭'‬t have a wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.01,0:45:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,‭ good thing I borrowed those‭ ‬weird five yen coins he had in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.81,0:45:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to go out of your way to return his stolen wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.93,0:45:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a problem if he'd made a fuss about it,‭ ‬wouldn‭'‬t it‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.03,0:45:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had his debit card and driving license in it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.03,0:46:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,‭ you should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.99,0:46:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that bug that you slipped into the‭ ‬FBI kitten's sleeve when she grabbed your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.95,0:46:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.51,0:46:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.49,0:46:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.77,0:46:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get anything interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.62,0:46:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...from that kitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.93,0:46:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was quite the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.32,0:46:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got to hear a surprising inside story.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.58,0:46:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You‭'‬ll let me hear the outcome of that story,‭ ‬won‭'‬t you‭?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.59,0:46:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, as soon as I‭'‬ve obtained‭ ‬positive proof of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.96,0:46:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can already say‭ this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.65,0:46:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a terrifying man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.46,0:46:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.81,0:46:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leading near the Bell Tree Tower, a strange multi-dimensional request!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.70,0:46:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solve the riddle of the unusual party!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.82,0:47:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan: The Coded Invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.32,0:47:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airs at 6 PM on Saturday 19th April!
